707455f-a.title: Brooklyn: Wyckoff Ave. - Madison St.
707455f-a.text:
WWyckoff Ave., south side, west from Madison Street to Myrtle
Ave. (elevated structure thereon), showing a group of buildings be-
longing to Welz and 2erweck, brewers. These buildings were razed in
1926.
June 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
